{% block content %}
    
    <div class="header-box">
        <h1 class="header--species" lang="en-US">{{ species[0].name }}</h1>
        <h2 class="header--name" lang="en-US">{{ species[0].commonName }}</h2>
        <h2 class="header--name">{{ species[0].chineseName }}</h2>
        <h3 class="header--status">{{ species[0].statusChinese }}</h3>
        <h4 class="header--danger">{{ species[0].dangerChinese }}</h4>
    </div>                      

    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-modal_zh.njk" %}
    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-nonModal_zh.njk" %}
    {% include "partials/_swiper-responsive-images-thumbs_zh.njk" %}

    <div class="text-box-container">
        <div class="text-box--species-media">
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    更多美圖
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://blog.sina.com.tw/d100vs/article.php?pbgid=30839&entryid=241459">好期待能再遇見台灣標蛇 - 轉自 自然生活記趣</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/x0001882/article?mid=2832&prev=2877&next=2806&l=a&fid=37&sc=1">野外探險 台灣標蛇 - 轉自 志明的蛇王國</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-box-container text-box-container-info">
        <div class="text-box--species">
            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    家族
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    黃頷蛇科，<span lang="en-US">Xenoderminae</span> 亞種
                    <br>
                    <span lang="en-US">Colubridae, subfamily Xenoderminae</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    最大體長
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    90 cm
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    台灣棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
 	                台灣全島海拔 1000 - 2000 m 可見。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    世界棲地分布
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
 	                台灣特有亞種。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    外觀描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text" lang="en-US">
                    Small snake; total length up to 90 cm. Whole body is iridescent under light. There are 23-29 (mostly 27 at mid-body) rows of scales, which are keeled throughout body (and tail). The scales of an outermost row in upper face of postcloacal region are not much enlarged when compared with adjacent scales. Head is small, oval and not distinct from neck; body is slender; tail is moderately short. Eye is small, bead-like; iris is black, indistinct since it blends with dark head and pupil is round, black, and blends with rest of eye. Tongue has reddish stem and diffuse gray fork tips whose base is dark brown. The frontal is slightly broader than long; the parietal is nearly twice as long as broad and contacted posterolaterally by an enlarged paraparietal scale. Upper head, body and tail is uniform olive (dark-edged in anterior part of scale), grayish tan, or black. There is a dark longitudinal line on mid-dorsal row of scales on body and tail. Ventral surface is olive-yellow (dark-edged in anterior part of scale) or dark gray; the color is slightly darker on tail than on body. Whole body is usually black in the young. Anal scale is entire, and subcaudals are not divided.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    生態描述
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text"> 	
                    標蛇為夜行性陸棲蛇類，喜歡居住在潮濕的環境，像是山林底層、亂石縫與落葉堆中。以蚯蚓與蛞蝓為主食，也有可能會捕食青蛙。攻擊性弱，甚少有相關的襲擊紀錄。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    學名與俗名
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        <span lang="en-US"><i>Achalinus</i></span> 來自希臘文意義不詳。史氏(<span lang="en-US">Stejneger</span>) 所著的 "日本本土與鄰近區域的兩棲爬蟲(<span lang="en-US">Herpetology of Japan and Adjacent Territory</span>)" 解釋為 "<span lang="en-US"><i>chalinos</i></span>"，意思是"籠頭(套在馬頭上的輔具)"。
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-box-paragraph">
                        <span lang="en-US"><i>formosanus</i></span> 則是拉丁文有 "來自台灣"的意思。
                    </div>
                    台灣標蛇、台灣脊蛇。
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="species-info-box">
                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    相關連結
                </div>
                <ul class="my-list2 info-box-text my-list-1--species">
                    <li lang="en-US"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://reptile-database.reptarium.cz/species.php?genus=Achalinus&species=formosanus" lang="en-US">Reptile Database</a></li>
                    <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.jstor.org/pss/1445485">重新定義分類標蛇並且介紹一個新亞種 - <span lang="en-US">Taxonomic re-definition of <i>Achalinus formosanus</i>, with description of a new subspecies. (Ota, H. and Toyama, M. 1989.)</span></a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="translator-name">翻譯:周信甫</div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Swiper JS -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Initialize Swiper -->
    <script   src="js/mySwiper.min.js"></script>

{% endblock %}